title: New Creator: Gary Henderson
body:
Name: Gary Henderson

Socials: https://twitter.com/GaryLHenderson
https://www.digitalmarketing.org/

Info: Owner of digital marketing community DigitalMarketing.org.  Creating consistent content for his lifetime membership program, coaching clients, blog, two podcasts, public facing IG, FB, LinkedIn and Clubhouse profiles, and growing rapidly.  

Use Cases:
Incorporating coin giveaways and transaction use cases around his book launch, as well as on his podcasts, and existing paid transaction/subscription programs. 

Community Treasury Grant Tier: $1,000

A 'yes' will approve Gary with a $1,000 Community Treasury Gift Coin grant.

A 'no' will deny this proposal.
